                        </tbody>
                    </table>

                    <h4><span>How and for what purposes do we use your survey data?</span></h4>
                    <p><span>Based on your </span><b>survey data</b><span> we create a unique profile on our website </span><b><a target="_blank" href="<?=$host?>"><?=$ihost?></a></b><span> and in the SpinCRM mobile app, which we use to identify you as a registered user of the </span><b>website <a target="_blank" href="<?=$host?>"><?=$ihost?></a></b><span> and SpinCRM mobile app and which will give you the ability to use the Services under the terms and conditions defined in the Rules and/or this Policy.</span></p>
                    <p><span>Based on the </span><b>data you provide</b><span> we also recognize you when, for example, you want to update or change your data, contact us regarding certain personal information, rights related to personal data processing, etc.</span></p>
                    <p><span>We also use the </span><b>contact details</b><span> (email, phone number) you provide in the survey for communication purposes, including responding to your requests, comments, providing you with important information about the Services, their provision and/or changes to this Policy, contacting you in case the system unexpectedly experiences unforeseen issues.</span></p>
                    <p><span>It is very important that the data you provide in the survey is </span><b>accurate and correct</b><span>. If you provide </span><b>incorrect (fake) data</b><span>, forget it or do not update changed data, it may be difficult for us to ensure the provision of Services and problems may arise in the implementation of your rights. We will not be liable in any way for damages incurred by you due to providing incorrect or incomplete personal data.</span></p>
                    <p><span>If your provided data changes, you must inform us immediately by updating the relevant data in the registration form on the website or mobile app. For information on </span><b>how to update your changed survey data</b><span>, please refer to section 5.2 of this Policy.</span></p>
                    <p><b>The company will not have the ability to verify the accuracy and conformity to reality of the data you provide.</b><span> By accepting your registration survey, we will consider your data to be accurate and correct, and all your consents to be given of your free will after fully reviewing this Policy and Rules.</span></p>
                    <h3><span>1.2. Offering proposals and information</span></h3>
                    <p><span>If when filling out the registration survey you </span><b>agreed to receive offers and news,</b><span> we process your personal data by providing you with such offers and information, e.g. general newsletters, information about our and our partners' offers, discounts, promotions, contests, chances to win prizes, requests for your opinion about the services and products provided, etc. We provide offers and information in your profile and mobile app, as well as by other means you choose: e.g. email, SMS messages.</span></p>

                    <table class="table">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><b>Personal data processed for the purpose of offering proposals and information:</b></td>
