                                <td><span>Term of data processing</span></td>
                                <td><span>For as long as your consent to receive offers and news remains valid. We may store your granted consent and evidence of it for a longer period if necessary in order to defend against claims, complaints or lawsuits brought against us.</span></td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <p><span>You can disagree to receive offers and news </span><b>at any time</b><span>, cancel them or change your chosen notification methods (channels). Your refusal to receive offers and news will </span><b>not prevent you from using the Services</b><span>. However, we want to warn you that some information is important for you, so we will send it without additional permissions, such as system updates, information about possible technical downtime or information about resolved system errors and similar information.</span></p> <h3><span>1.3. Statistics, market and customer behavior research</span></h3> <p><span>We constantly make every effort to improve our systems capabilities and help you optimize your work.</span></p>
                    <table class="table">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><b>Data processed for the purposes of statistics, market and customer behavior research:</b></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
